{"tid":293729,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《鄧寇克大行動》片長僅1小時47分鐘 Nolan成名後最短作品","createTime":"2017-06-22T11:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T12:43:55.000Z","uid":41453,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc1c4c24546f848958484361eb7ef7623208112","tid":293729,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"Nolan新片《鄧寇克大行動》片長僅為1小時47分鐘左右(包括片尾字幕的時間)。<br />\n<br />\n這是Nolan導演的第二短的作品，僅次於其處女作《Following》的69分鐘，比他最長的《Interstellar》少了整整62分鐘。與今年暑期檔其他大片對比：《變形金剛5》時長2小時29分鐘；《神奇女俠》時長2小時21分鐘，《銀河守衛隊2》時長2小時15分鐘，即將上映的《蜘蛛俠》據說也有2小時10分鐘。《鄧寇克大行動》107分鐘的片長可以說是相當的短了！<br />\n<br />\nNolan的作品時長都不短，2小時以上的影片居多，而且並沒有影響其票房成績。2012年的《蝙蝠俠：夜神起義》片場2小時44分鐘；2008年的《蝙蝠俠：黑夜之神》2小時32分鐘；2005年的《蝙蝠俠：俠影之謎》2小時20分鐘。這三部曲加起來全球票房超過24億美元。《Inception》2小時28分鐘，全球票房超過8億美元。"},{"pid":"d408b13dc1e52cfa4f68e055a06c474bac541c58","tid":293729,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪冇橋扭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48118aa76ddb64381831e4a7595a34929ad20ccd","tid":293729,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d6217a12a3feec2105b07c9c48108a07b06630","tid":293729,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪冇橋扭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該有60分鐘都係睇住班士兵望住個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi